    "It's a neutral day. Sometimes taking a quick 10-minute walk or drinking a glass of cold water can naturally elevate your baseline." : {
      "extractionState" : "manual",
      "localizations" : {
        "de" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Es ist ein neutraler Tag. Manchmal kann ein kurzer 10-minütiger Spaziergang oder das Trinken eines Glases kaltes Wasser Ihren Ausgangswert auf natürliche Weise erhöhen."
          }
        },
        "en" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "It's a neutral day. Sometimes taking a quick 10-minute walk or drinking a glass of cold water can naturally elevate your baseline."
          }
        },
        "es" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Es un día neutral. A veces, dar una caminata rápida de 10 minutos o beber un vaso de agua fría puede elevar naturalmente su nivel basal."
          }
        },
        "fr" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "C'est une journée neutre. Parfois, faire une marche rapide de 10 minutes ou boire un verre d’eau froide peut naturellement élever votre niveau de base."
          }
        },
        "it" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "È una giornata neutra. A volte fare una passeggiata veloce di 10 minuti o bere un bicchiere di acqua fredda può aumentare naturalmente i tuoi valori di base."
          }
        },
        "pt-PT" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "É um dia neutro. Às vezes, fazer uma caminhada rápida de 10 minutos ou beber um copo de água fria pode elevar naturalmente sua linha de base."
          }
        },
        "ru" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Нейтральный день. Иногда быстрая 10-минутная прогулка или стакан холодной воды могут естественным образом повысить ваш базовый уровень."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "It's best to track your measurements on the same day each week, at the same time and under the same circumstances." : {
      "comment" : "A description under the \"Weight-in\" toggle, explaining the importance of tracking weights at the same time each week.",
      "isCommentAutoGenerated" : true,
      "localizations" : {
        "de" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Es ist am besten, Ihre Messungen jede Woche am selben Tag, zur gleichen Zeit und unter den gleichen Umständen zu verfolgen."
          }
        },
        "es" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Lo mejor es realizar un seguimiento de sus medidas el mismo día de cada semana, a la misma hora y en las mismas circunstancias."
          }
        },
        "fr" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Il est préférable de suivre vos mesures le même jour chaque semaine, à la même heure et dans les mêmes circonstances."
          }
        },
        "it" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "È meglio monitorare le misurazioni lo stesso giorno ogni settimana, alla stessa ora e nelle stesse circostanze."
          }
        },
        "pt-PT" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "É melhor monitorar suas medições no mesmo dia da semana, no mesmo horário e nas mesmas circunstâncias."
          }
        },
        "ru" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Лучше всего отслеживать свои измерения в один и тот же день каждую неделю, в одно и то же время и при одних и тех же обстоятельствах."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Items created here are permanently saved to your database and can be used in your daily logs." : {
      "comment" : "A description below the form that explains that the ingredients created here are saved permanently and can be used in the user's daily logs.",
      "isCommentAutoGenerated" : true,
      "localizations" : {
